AIM:
To design a Student Registration Form using HTML5 & CSS3, store the entered data in a database table, and retrieve the stored student details using the SQL SELECT query.

PROCEDURE:
Start the code editor and create an HTML file for the registration form.
Apply basic CSS3 styles to improve appearance.
Create a MySQL database named studentdb.
Create a table students with fields — Name, Email, DOB, Department, Phone.
Write a PHP script insert.php to store the form data into the database.
Run the HTML form in a browser and submit details.
Use SQL SELECT * FROM students; to retrieve stored data.
Display the data on the screen or in phpMyAdmin.

code:
1) DataBase
